com.gemalto.idp.mobile.core

Class IdpResultCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gemalto.idp.mobile.core.IdpResultCode

  • public class IdpResultCode
extends java.lang.Object
    The definition of the Idp result codes.

    It gathers the codes for Core module, having one big list of potential problems.

    Since:
    4.0
